ục đắc Tây Hồ tiên sinh thư cảm tác kỳ 1 - 新到崑崙獄得西湖先生書感作其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hu%E1%BB%B3nh-Th%C3%BAc-Kh%C3%A1ng/author-tWIJ_JcBg9FILAgkriOf3g">Huỳnh Thúc Kháng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-25TiVNWxUWAtvZmhCPhLFQ">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/Vi-C%E1%BB%91-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Ti%C3%AAn-t%E1%BA%B7ng-ph%E1%BB%A5-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-bGdQDSjh1WP4i6FluaMuQw">Vi Cố Ngạn Tiên tặng phụ kỳ 1 - 為顧彥先贈婦其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/author-EfNc8fssq4nwf0WjqNOWdA">Lục Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/V%C5%A9-t%C3%ACnh-ng%E1%BA%A3i-m%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-NnpGB6dfbeS049KcZgPomA">Vũ tình ngải mạch - 雨晴刈麥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Th%C3%BAc-Tr%E1%BB%B1c/author-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Phan Thúc Trực</a>)<br></div>	</div>
